data.title: Shen mi fu qi (1991)
data.meta_description: Shen mi fu qi: Directed by Ziyu Li. With Hongsheng Jia, Wenli Jiang, Tang Li, Yanping Wang. Set in 1990s China, a newly wed young couple boarding on a luxury cruise for honeymoon. On an eventful night, the bride found herself in a stranger's bed after went back from public lavatory on-board the cruise, she was consequently raped.
